-- out/todo.txt --
minimal.a/b: pushdown reports cycle error (matching v2) instead of incomplete (v3).
small.p1: pushdown resolves #Y to {port: ""} (matching v2); #X still has cycle error.
medium.p1: pushdown resolves #Y and #X; Y gets cycle error.
large.p1: pushdown resolves #Y, #X, X; Y gets cycle error. Ordering sensitive.
